      • update

        public Optional<TrackInfo> update(String name,
                                  String artist,
                                  String album,
                                  byte[] albumCover,
                                  String coverFormat,
                                  String data,
                                  String year,
                                  String genre,
                                  String bmp,
                                  long duration)
        returns a trackinfo if some information was added and not overwritten (see isNew) AND a change occurred.
        Parameters:
        name - the name
        artist - the artist
        album - the album
        albumCover - the album cover
        coverFormat - the album cover format
        data - the data
        year - the year
        genre - the genre
        duration - the duration
        bmp - the bmp
        Returns:
        a trackInfo if some information was updated, and an empty optional if: 1. information would be ovewritten or 2. no change occured
